1
00:01:27,039 --> 00:01:28,039
Are you that

2
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,640
old man who sells books?

3
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:33,600
Am I that ugly?

4
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,880
Lu Sinian,

5
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:37,650
long time no see.

6
00:01:39,759 --> 00:01:40,960
You've seen it.

7
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:43,800
Don't you like it?

8
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:46,140
That recurring dream of mine,

9
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,479
is it your doing?

10
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:49,479
And,

11
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:52,020
after coming here,

12
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:54,160
the dream changed.

13
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,000
Why is that?

14
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,960
Both dreams

15
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:01,010
are memories of your past life.

16
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,560
Do you not believe me,

17
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:06,800
or do you not believe that Yuyao would kill you?

18
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:10,130
Whether I believe it or not is my business.

19
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,340
First, tell me,

20
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:12,740
who are you?

21
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,020
I forgot to introduce myself.

22
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,480
My name is Xuanqing.

23
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:18,800
We

24
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,720
are old acquaintances.

25
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,410
Old acquaintances?

26
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,200
You lured me here.

27
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,640
What is your purpose?

28
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,250
What do you want?

29
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,200
Lu Sinian.

30
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:30,880
Lu Sinian.

31
00:02:32,079 --> 00:02:32,680
Lu Sinian!

32
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:35,240
Bo Peak reflects the snow's glow.

33
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,440
The Jade Pool ripples gently.

34
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:41,560
Lotuses bloom with a millennial love.

35
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:45,800
An endless affection that never fades.

36
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,079
Sinian!

37
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:48,640
Sinian!

38
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,850
I just saw an anomaly in the sky.

39
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,100
Did you see anyone?

40
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:54,680
Are you hurt?

41
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,040
No.

42
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,940
You scared me to death.

43
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,460
I thought it was some anomaly.

44
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:04,360
An anomaly?

45
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,040
Yes,

46
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:14,760
an anomaly.

47
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,760
I

48
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,820
know how to read the stars.

49
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,980
The celestial signs I just saw

50
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,220
were a bit unusual.

51
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:25,079
There might be a bloody disaster.

52
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,560
So I rushed to pick you up.

53
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,090
Let's go down the mountain.

54
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,480
Xuanqing

55
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,720
left because he was afraid

56
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,600
of running into Yuyao.

57
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,520
Why did he run away?

58
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:48,930
I seem to have just remembered something.

59
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,920
I think I saw at the bottom of the water

60
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:52,880
a mass of

61
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:54,720
something black.

62
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,600
Is that

63
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,160
what you called

64
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:02,080
an anomaly?

65
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:05,800
Then we really need to go down the mountain!

66
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,480
It's your first time here, so you don't know.

67
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:08,320
Around here,

68
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:10,840
there's a legend that's been passed down.

69
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,520
In that water,

70
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:16,519
there is a terrifying,

71
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:18,959
inherently brutal water monster.

72
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,200
The kind that kills

73
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,440
and eats people.

74
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:29,340
I'd rather believe she is just the way she looks now.

75
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,480
If she's been pretending all along,

76
00:04:32,159 --> 00:04:34,159
then she's acting a little too well.

77
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,800
Maybe she

78
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,320
isn't that scheming.

79
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,480
Yueyue,

80
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:58,940
can't you be a little understanding?

81
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,280
I'm busy with work right now,

82
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:01,720
and the project is under a lot of pressure.

83
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,480
Didn't I bring you to Tianchi?

84
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,800
Do you call this keeping me company?

85
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,600
You've been answering and making calls the whole time.

86
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,000
You are always working.

87
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:10,040
I want someone

88
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,880
who can keep me company and care for me,

89
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:12,240
not a

90
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,970
workaholic who is always busy.

91
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,320
My career is on the rise right now.

92
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,480
I have to deal with these things.

93
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,160
Career on the rise.

94
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,640
Then when will things settle down?

95
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,800
When can we actually live a normal life?

96
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,720
Who says I don't want to live our lives?

97
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,760
Don't I have to pay the car loan and mortgage?

98
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:32,400
Don't I have to pay for water, electricity, and heating?

99
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,080
Stop guilt-tripping me.

100
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:36,340
You say the same things every day.

101
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,360
What's the point?

102
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,320
There is no point.

103
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,730
Then let's break up.

104
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,890
Who's afraid of who?

105
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,040
Fine, let's break up.

106
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:44,970
Don't regret it.

107
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:03,240
Listen up, whatever's in the water.

108
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:05,170
No matter what monster you are,

109
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:06,040
tonight,

110
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,480
I will stand guard here.

111
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,780
Let's see what moves you make.

112
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:12,240
Yuyao,

113
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,600
long time no see.

114
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:14,760
Oh no,

115
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,680
I should say,

116
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,760
it's been 98 lifetimes.

117
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,440
Xuanqing.

118
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,210
I didn't expect it to be you.

119
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,920
There's a lot you didn't expect.

120
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,080
You're so obsessed with love,

121
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:34,010
your magic progresses too slowly.

122
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:36,000
You couldn't find Lu Sinian,

123
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,280
so I found him for you,

124
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,840
and lured him here.

125
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,240
Shouldn't you

126
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,240
thank me properly?

127
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,880
What did you do to Lu Sinian?

128
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,000
Don't worry.

129
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,720
I am helping you.

130
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,760
He has reincarnated for 98 lifetimes,

131
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:52,080
and you still can't forget him.

132
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:53,640
This 99th lifetime

133
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,680
is your last chance.

134
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,810
Whether it's the last chance or not

135
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:01,040
is not up to you.

136
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,440
The love and hate in this world,

137
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,080
who dictates it?

138
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,160
The Queen Mother?

139
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,760
Couples in this world...

140
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:13,200
Some are childhood sweethearts

141
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:14,480
who grow old together.

142
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,490
Some fall in love at first sight

143
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:18,240
and stay together like birds on the wing.

144
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,000
Others

145
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,640
love each other deeply

146
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,480
and make eternal vows.

147
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:25,880
Of course,

148
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:27,980
there are also some

149
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,890
who cast off the old for the new,

150
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,400
change their minds,

151
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,940
and fall for someone else.

152
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,640
Tell me,

153
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:37,159
shouldn't they be punished?

154
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:41,000
Under this Sea-Calming Needle you guard,

155
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:43,600
lie the love spirits

156
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,240
of so many couples.

157
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,690
If I borrow a little,

158
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:48,120
what's the harm?

159
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,100
Don't even think about it!

160
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:54,120
Yuyao.

161
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,920
Time is running out for you.

162
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:23,000
Why is there no breakfast today?

163
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,000
Boss.

164
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:27,920
Yuyao.

165
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:39,440
I'll go get something to eat myself.

166
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:00,400
Thank you.

167
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:01,300
Here you go.

168
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:07,820
I actually didn't have that dream again last night.

169
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:09,920
So where did this dream come from?

170
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:22,280
Young man, come here.

171
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:24,850
Where is that pretty girl with you?

172
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:26,480
Why didn't she come with you?

173
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:27,440
Ma'am,

174
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:28,960
are you talking about...

175
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,690
The boss of the clothing store.

176
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:33,000
To meet you,

177
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,290
she was picking and choosing here.

178
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:39,240
In our Kazakh legends,

179
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,320
the snow lotus

180
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:42,920
represents pure love.

181
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,080
The girls

182
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,520
will take that whip

183
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:47,970
and chase their lovers.

184
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:52,360
Come here.

185
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,420
Take a look at this.

186
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:56,200
Look at this hairpin.

187
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:58,120
Look at its tassel,

188
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,930
doesn't it look like a whip?

189
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,800
Young man.

190
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,280
Don't be shy.

191
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,360
My eyes are not wrong.

192
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:27,410
This girl treats you very well.

193
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:28,640
You must hold on to her.

194
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:29,280
Ma'am,

195
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:30,970
we just met not long ago.

196
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,280
But,

197
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:36,560
it feels like we've known each other for a long time.

198
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,360
Right.

199
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:39,520
It's good to grow fond of each other over time.

200
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:41,080
Buy a gift for the girl.

201
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:42,650
I'll get one for you.

202
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:46,160
Let me show you our intangible cultural heritage crafts.

203
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:47,840
Kazakh embroidery.

204
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:50,090
Take a look at these embroidered bags.

205
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,690
What about this person?

206
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:55,800
This doll.

207
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,960
Hello.

208
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,100
Is boss Yu Yao here?

209
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:09,200
Our boss went to Dinghai Shenzhen to fix something.

210
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,060
Fix something?

211
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:12,280
Fix what?

212
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:16,380
Practicing cultivation.

213
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,120
Thanks.
